snippet: The court on Wednesday ordered the extradition to the United States of Dmitry Ustinov, a Russian suspected of illegal arms dealing.
abstract: Lithuanian court orders extradition to the United States of Dmitry Ustinov, Russian man suspected of illegal arms dealing.
